  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nErigon version: `2022.10.01`\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nRPC daemon starts as separate process\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\nErigon logs are fine but RPC daemon logs show an error loop:\r\n\r\n```\r\n[INFO] [10-05|13:38:04.622] DB schemas compatible                    reader=6.0.0 database=6.0.0\r\n[INFO] [10-05|13:38:04.636] Use --snapshots=false\r\n[INFO] [10-05|13:38:04.636] rpc filters: subscribing to Erigon events\r\n[EROR] [10-05|13:38:04.636] Could not connect to DB                  err=\"create aggregator: ReopenFiles: NewHistory: accounts, NewInvertedIndex: accounts, open /home/erigon/erigon-sepolia-data/snapshots/history: no such file or directory\"\r\n```\r\n\r\nRestarting the RPC daemon process does not fix it",
